com.shipdream.lib.poke

Interface Provider.OnFreedListener

  • Enclosing class:
    Provider<T>

    public static interface Provider.OnFreedListener
    Listener will be called when the given provider is not referenced by any objects. The listener will be called before its cached instance is freed if there is a cache associated.
